  "response": "There are several well-regarded textbooks for Chemistry for 12th ISC (Indian School Certificate) students. A popular choice among students and educators is:\n\n1. **Nootan ISC Chemistry for Class 12 by Dr. H.C. Srivastava** - This book covers the ISC syllabus comprehensively and is known for its clear explanations and illustrative examples.\n\nOther commonly recommended books include:\n2. **Selina Concise Chemistry Class 12** - This is another good choice that aligns with the ISC curriculum and provides thorough coverage of topics.\n3. **Modern\u2019s ABC of Chemistry for Class 12** - Known for its detailed explanations and practice problems.\n\nIt's often helpful to also refer to additional study guides and practice books to supplement your understanding and preparation for exams.",
